			,Insurance_Score_2
			,Insurance_Score_Desc_2
			,Lob_Desc
			,New_Business_Entry_Date
			,New_Renewal_Desc

			,Policy_Key
			,Policy_Symbol
			,Producer_Code
			,Secondary_Home_Desc
			,Policy_Number
			,Insurance_Score_Year
			,Insurance_Score_2_Year
